features: ✅【Upgraded Folding Installation】- No screws, no drilling design! Our upgraded over the toilet storage features a folding design, unfold the product, secure it with a non-marking adhesive, and it's ready to use. The installation takes less than 1 minute and no holes need to be drilled to destroy the wall! Make assembly a breeze. When you're not using the shelf, you can fold it up for storage to save space.

✅【Sturdy Metal Material】- This over toilet storage shelf is made of sturdy metal material with strong load-bearing capacity. The outer layer is coated with water-resistant paint, which is less likely to rust and lasts longer than other over the toilet shelves. The high-density mesh design allows air circulation, reduces dust buildup, ensures breathability and odor-free. The raised guard rail prevents items from falling and guards your bottles and jars.

✅【Space Saving】- For small bathrooms, this 2-tier over toilet organizer is the perfect space-saving solution. It can hold more bathroom essentials such as shampoo, body wash, towels, toilet paper, soap and face wash. With the unique floral pattern, the above toilet storage beautifies your bathroom space and makes your bathroom neat and elegant.

✅【Multifunctional Toilet Shelf】- Our bathroom organizer over toilet storage comes with an additional metal basket and adjustable paper holder, perfect for storing toilet paper, toothpaste, toothbrushes, combs, and other small items. This toilet rack is perfect for bathroom, laundry room, living room, balcony, kitchen, restroom, etc.

✅【Universal Size】- Our bathroom shelves over toilet size: 12.8"*6.5"*15.55", fits most standard toilets and maximizes the vertical space above the toilet. The bottom shelf is 2.6" from the toilet, enough height to allow you to easily press the flush button, ensuring convenient and hassle-free use.

✅【Widely Applicable】- The versatility of this shelf makes it a must-have for any home storage. It can be used as an over the toilet organizer, bathroom organizer countertop, kitchen spice rack, cosmetic storage rack, etc. If you have any questions about Iirios bathroom shelves over toilet, please contact us, and we will reply and solve your problem within 24 hours.

manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Iirios 2-Tier Folding Over Toilet Storage Rack - Say Goodbye to Bathroom Clutter! Do you often struggle with the clutter in your small bathroom?Are you often unable to find the toiletries you need? The upgrade over the toilet storage is a decorative storage solution to optimize your bathroom space. It can effectively store your bathroom essentials and make your bathroom stylish and elegant. Perfect for storing bathroom supplies, cosmetics, toiletries, kitchen spice bottles, stationery and other kinds of items, widely used in bathrooms, toilets, bedrooms, kitchens, laundry rooms, offices and other indoor places.

Folding Installation: Just unfold the product and use it, equipped with 2 adhesive stickers, takes less than a minute! Installation Note: Transparent non-marking adhesive pads are suitable for pasting on smooth surfaces (such as tiles, marble, glass, metal, mirrors), not suitable for rough surfaces (plaster walls, wall tiles, rustic tiles, mosaics, lime walls).

With raised guard rails, the bathroom organizer over toilet storage can better protect your items from falling and guard your bottles. The bottom shelf is 2.56" from the toilet, which does not affect the use of the toilet button at all. The size fits most standard toilets. The high-density mesh design is easy to drain, waterproof and rust-proof. Made of all-metal material to ensure durability and lifespan.

The extra metal basket can store toothpaste, toothbrushes and combs, etc. You can put more daily necessities on this bathroom shelf organizer. The detachable paper holder is available on both sides. Hanging on the rack does not take up any space, making the necessities within reach. The bottom is equipped with 2 non-marking stickers, no need to drill holes, firmly attached to the toilet countertop, making the storage shelf more stable.
